txt.en: You should return to Thurindol and inform him of your deeds within The Towers of the Teeth.

Those who dwell in The Towers of the Teeth are numerous. Driving off even a fraction of their number will better position the Host of the West to travel safely through The Wastes.\n\n<rgb=#FF0000>Warning: This quest requires Towers of the Teeth: Guardian of the Depths to be underway. If that quest has been completed or failed, you will be unable to exit and re-enter this instance in order to complete this quest.</rgb>
'You have done well, friend. Your efforts will be duly noted!'
